@node linkAbout "About"
About
----------

Hollywood Soccer Manager - Editor is a program to maintain the database behind the yet to come soccersimulation.
The Editor is written with the help of Airsofts Hollywood.

@{"AirsoftSoftwair Website" system "OPENURL http://www.airsoftsoftwair.de/en/index.html"}
You can maintain all essential data with the editor, thus you can influence how the game works.
The data is the base for all simulationresults.
You have the option to edit data of the following categories:
@{I}Nations
Leagues
Events
Clubs
Players
Coaches
Referees
@{UI}
More about this in the following chapters
@endnode

